description: Benny Boy's catering can handle your small backyard BBQ or your large wedding with thousands of people. Our specialty is smoked meats but Benny Boy himself (Ben Maas) is a professionally trained and experienced executive chef than can do anything when it comes to food. Fruit Carvings, Pastas, Seafood, you name it, he can do it better than anyone else around.Recently Benny Boy's Food Truck opened up and is currently at Bump's Bar in Owatonna. That is of course when it isn't going to and from big caters and other events. The food truck is a quick stop for lunch when you want real food from a real chef. Stop by today and get some flavor!!
name: Benny Boy's Catering
